207    private final String text;
208
209    Permission(final @NonNull String text) {
210        this.text = text;
211    }
212
213    @Override
214    public String toString() {
215        return this.text;
216    }
217
218    public String format(Object... replacements) {
219        return String.format(this.toString(), replacements);
220    }
